	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />The influences also seem to vary a bit. A lot of japanese-made NES soundtracks sound like they's been inspired a lot by metal / hard rock. 
<br />
<br />The european musicians on the other hand were probably inspired more by synth and techno music. And in some cases folk music, or whatever you should call it (think Solstice and Asterix).
<br />
<br />As for american-made NES soundtracks.. I can't name a single good one (no offense to the creators).

		

		</td>
	</tr>
