	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />A LOT of Japanese game music was influenced by either rock/metal, YMO, or Casiopea, so the styles tend to get really close to those bands (if you check them out.)  For European music, look to 80s electro, dance, house, pop (and rock) for influences.  Also, progressive rock and Jean-Michel Jarre get their own categories.   <img src="./images/smilies/icon_biggrin.gif" alt=":-D" title="Very Happy" />

		

		</td>
